      "content": "thaw the frozen parts? i dont think that's possible. i feel like i've reached the end of the road. it's just exhausting, pretending to be alive when you know the soul of you is already buried. it feels more like carrying around a corpse than being a person. why should i keep dragging this heavy, empty thing around if it serves no purpose?",
